Library Management System

This is a simple command-line library system built with Python and SQLite.
You can add books, register members, borrow and return books.

Commands

-add_book → Add a new book

-view_books → Show all books

-add_member → Add a new member

-view_members → Show all members

-borrow → Borrow a book

-return → Return a book

-view_borrowed → Show books borrowed by a member

-exit → Exit the program

Notes

Data is stored in library.db (created automatically).

Delete library.db if you want to reset the system.